# Two triangles, two solid-color materials (red + blue), NO textures / NO UVs.
# Exercises the MTL-Kd -> per-vertex color import path (no texture fallback).
mtllib two-material.mtl
v 0.0 0.0 0.0
v 1.0 0.0 0.0
v 1.0 1.0 0.0
v 0.0 1.0 0.0
vn 0.0 0.0 1.0
usemtl red
f 1//1 2//1 3//1
usemtl blue
f 1//1 3//1 4//1
